data.enText: a period of time in which you sit or lie in a small room (also called a sauna ) which has been heated to a very high temperature by burning coal or wood. Some saunas involve the use of steam.

data.chText: 带游泳池和桑拿浴室的旅馆
data.enText: a hotel with a swimming pool and sauna

tr: steam is produced by pouring water over heated rocks

value.def: If you have a sauna, you sit or lie in a room that is so hot that it makes you sweat. People have saunas in order to relax and to clean their skin thoroughly.
A sauna is a room or building where you can have a sauna.
